{"tid":1911074,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"1月遊峨眉　疑為精舍爆疫源頭 男住持佛堂釋病毒","createTime":"2020-03-05T06:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T06:16:22.000Z","uid":290118,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"66c7e5d0c0781428c92a49906303a81a661f0e77","tid":1911074,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:05:58.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】本港昨新增四宗確診感染武漢肺炎個案，累計增至105宗，其中兩宗個案來自北角福慧精舍的佛堂群組，包括43歲佛堂男住持（第102宗），及早前確診居於紅山半島佛堂女善信的57歲外傭（第103宗），兩人均無病徵，該群組至今有18宗確診。據悉，該佛堂男住持1月農曆新年前，曾先後到訪內地廈門及四川峨眉山。有感染及傳染病醫生指，若該患者血清只驗出抗體免疫球蛋白G（IgG），即可能是很早期感染，不排除是佛堂群組感染源頭。<br />\n記者：謝明明 陳沛冰 于健民<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200305/6CT5GOUUNSKLLSRCY3MHQMOKM4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200305%2F6CT5GOUUNSKLLSRCY3MHQMOKM4%2F&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq3wvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=dc5940f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200305%2F6CT5GOUUNSKLLSRCY3MHQMOKM4%2F&h=b6ba5de2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200305/6CT5GOUUNSKLLSRCY3MHQMOKM4/</a><br />\n<br />\n貧僧法號釋病毒，阿彌陀佛🙏"},{"pid":"14a9f87f7f311b4327fade2fc546a9c7663d475e","tid":1911074,"uid":60136,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:10:56.000Z","msg":"釋毒尊"},{"pid":"8a93811497711802e8d7795d2e0a488752a2bab6","tid":1911074,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾時中醫都會染病"},{"pid":"305c39fcf13802cd551bc2237bc0d8d7d0ec08c5","tid":1911074,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T06:14:29.000Z","msg":"方仗你點睇今次精役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660ba880d0ca87a0344f8cf037754dad631ed96b","tid":1911074,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"14a9f87f7f311b4327fade2fc546a9c7663d475e","tid":191107